Title: What's Up, Doc?
Writer: Buck Henry (screenplay), David Newman (screenplay), Robert Benton (screenplay), Peter Bogdanovich (story)
Actors: Barbra Streisand, Ryan O'Neal, Madeline Kahn, Kenneth Mars
Plot: The accidental mix-up of four identical plaid overnight bags leads to a series of increasingly wild and wacky situations.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 1 win.
